@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080
@sourceId = 1
@archiveRuleId = 1

### AI 自动发现并导入采集源
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sources/discover
Content-Type: application/json

{"topic":"人工智能","language":"zh-CN","count":10,"quality":"权威"}

### 刷新单个采集源状态
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sources/{{sourceId}}/health

### 刷新全部启用采集源状态
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sources/health/refresh

### 查询最近七天的成功任务
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tasks?status=SUCCESS&from=2026-07-12&to=2026-07-18&page=0&size=20

### 查询归档资料
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/articles?archived=true&page=0&size=20

### 新增归档整理规则
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/archive-rules
Content-Type: application/json

{"name":"AI 高质量资料","keyword":"AI","minQuality":80,"sortOrder":10,"enabled":true}

### 查看整理规则
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/archive-rules

### 删除整理规则
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/archive-rules/{{archiveRuleId}}
